data.description: This is simply a great house. Well maintained and low maintenance. There is a slope down the driveway, but it sets on a beautifully level yard! Large, level backyard that is partially fenced. As you enter the front door, you are welcomed by a lovely spacious living room that has an open concept to the kitchen and dining areas. The home features somewhat of a split bedroom floor plan. Along with the main bedroom and bathroom to the left as you walk into the front door, there is one additional bedroom. To the right, past the living, dining, and kitchen areas are the other two bedrooms, guest bath, and garage. The layout of this home, in my opinion, couldn't have been thought through any better. It seems to be perfect for a first time home buyer, growing family, a completed family looking to relocate, or older individuals looking for a ranch. This property has so much to offer! Don't miss out, schedule your private showing today!
